Package: kingcounty
Title: King County, WA Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for King County, WA Socrata Open Data portal.
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for pets, crime, food inspections,
    water quality, property tax, elections, and 245+ county datasets.
